  "pages": [
    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Last night the city council fin.\nally passed the franchise granting\nthe Northern Pacific right to lay\na new transfer track between that\nroad the Inland Empire system and\nthe Great Northern, running east\nof the Schade brewery.\n\n\nThis matter has been pending for\nfour years. 1t is now reported that\nthe Northern Pacific intends to run\ntheir regular trains over the new\nline some day into the Great\nNorthern depot. giving the Hill\nlines one union depot."
    }
